ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"Saboteur"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"冇警守嘅地方。我在暗，敵在明，手腳夠快匿得埋，佢地唔會搵到。<br />\n利申，千祈唔好"},{"pid":"8935e73b1a2a0b58268d4b227525759be53c2092","tid":1529443,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"呢個運動已經進入消㲖戰階段 war of attrition <br />\n<br />\n抗爭佐三個月。我地用人力 物力有手足俾拘捕。大家已有倦意。以後要有針對性計劃 圍狗屋要快閃 警力一集結就返屋企 野貓魔法師係低成本效益  星期六日唔同地區集會減低對狗鐵依賴同牽制警力<br />\n<br />\n共狗黑警有無限資源。但瘋狂OT. 呢一個星期已經開始爆煲  鳩拉狂燥。同埋狗策略係大量狗去製造非對稱力量 所以一定要be water. <br />\n<br />\n最係我地對狗humint (human intelligence) 係極小。三萬隻犬又話好多仲有良知。大家如果有針 唔該利用下。不外乎用ego (話差佬行動快清得好 問下點解） 一係用同情心（抗爭者好慘情 你好人提下水） 或者溝女警犬 pump her for information <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知大家好攰 不過已經無退路<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"db9a57947df377d8f516150965f4db64e1f02d21","tid":1529443,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa328fa350b743048741ed2a747ce03030c5fffe","tid":1529443,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02d28d1c69629fc6d2a064c8f51b1040738221c2","tid":1529443,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c8cd0976f10fd6588732c954489984d3d9e9268","tid":1529443,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c3833ee3e52f21ad97dc462074e6045cd45ae83","tid":1529443,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"Saboteur"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"冇警守嘅地方。我在暗，敵在明，手腳夠快匿得埋，佢地唔會搵到。<br />\n利申，千祈唔好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3f3dc1603fe4854bc49a5857ebc270df328822","tid":1529443,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"記住<br />\n<br />\nSituation awareness 即係注意現場<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好乜都唔做。不時OODA<br />\n<br />\nObserve 觀察<br />\nOrient 知道身處地方位置，<br />\ndecide 做決定<br />\nAct 行動<br />\n<br />\n重複不斷"},{"pid":"c858ddfd00f8bb6717f887318c6b7b524e350c0d","tid":1529443,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"本身齊腳都難打啦，上左裝咪又係得幾十個肯打"},{"pid":"bae9ba777f55fbc6053693578173177364ed5e4f","tid":1529443,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d70d3cee663bdfb424d6ba9e13fdc573aaffcb57","tid":1529443,"uid":22624,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e73a3788e9ff5e406ebc09681afe02f07f8b41c2","tid":1529443,"uid":49316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"872f0a71f49a5bf6393d7a4d3319cb3f7a0ffc13","tid":1529443,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"地區好難打<br />\n全部唔上裝咁出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"地區上裝真係未必夠人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"地區街坊圍屌就夠，精神轟炸班狗，唔需要硬拼，敵進我退，敵駐我擾，一出狗就即散，咁先係be water"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:31:20.000Z","msg":"街坊都會照噴胡椒水/出煙。。。（琴晚太子警署） 點夠打？？"},{"pid":"7b8971802d510bcb8e493b0d098681c4951f0aaf","tid":1529443,"uid":256812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d70d3cee663bdfb424d6ba9e13fdc573aaffcb57","tid":1529443,"uid":22624,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e73a3788e9ff5e406ebc09681afe02f07f8b41c2","tid":1529443,"uid":49316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"872f0a71f49a5bf6393d7a4d3319cb3f7a0ffc13","tid":1529443,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"地區好難打<br />\n全部唔上裝咁出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"地區上裝真係未必夠人"},